                <p>In 2013 I spent several months designing, testing and revising a <a href="https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/154554/race-til-thorin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">card-based board game</a>, which contains many of the same elements as RPG Games, but without the need for preparation or acting out characters. As I lacked the artistic talents to illustrate it I was helped by Jaime Buckley who let me use the characters and setting from his books.</p>
